name: Bubu
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Bubu and Dudu are on a mission to unite and empower the crypto community. Through innovative tokenomics, we prioritize rewarding our holders and encouraging long-term engagement. By staking tokens, holders contribute to stability, reduce sell pressure, and receive incentives. We promote fairness, transparency, and collaboration by distributing rewards from our vault to randomly staked holders.
